# Inside IR Ferrovial — environment variables
# The app runs fully WITHOUT any keys (Yahoo Finance covers prices, history,
# technicals, fundamentals, peers and calendar). Keys only enrich the News feed.

# Optional: free Finnhub API key (https://finnhub.io/register) for richer,
# deduplicated company news. Add it in Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables.
FINNHUB_API_KEY=
